<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <title>Vérification 2FA | MedFlow</title>

  <link href="{{ asset('assets/img/favicon.png') }}" rel="icon">
  <link href="{{ asset('assets/vendor/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css') }}" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="{{ asset('assets/vendor/bootstrap-icons/bootstrap-icons.css') }}" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    :root{
      --mf-primary:#0097B2;
      --mf-primary-rgb:0,151,178;
      --mf-blue:#003399;
      --mf-blue-rgb:0,51,153;
      --mf-surface:#ffffff;
      --mf-border:rgba(15,23,42,.10);
      --mf-shadow:0 24px 70px rgba(2,6,23,.14);
    }
    body{
      min-height:100vh;
      background: radial-gradient(1200px 700px at 20% 10%, rgba(var(--mf-primary-rgb), .16), transparent 55%),
                  radial-gradient(900px 600px at 90% 0%, rgba(var(--mf-blue-rgb), .12), transparent 55%),
                  #f8fafc;
    }
    .mf-shell{min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:32px 16px;}
    .mf-card{
      width:100%;
      max-width:520px;
      border:1px solid var(--mf-border);
      border-radius:18px;
      background:var(--mf-surface);
      box-shadow:var(--mf-shadow);
      overflow:hidden;
    }
    .mf-head{
      padding:18px 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(var(--mf-primary-rgb), .18), rgba(var(--mf-blue-rgb), .10));
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--mf-border);
    }
    .mf-logo{
      display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
      font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.2px;
    }
    .mf-logo i{color:var(--mf-primary)}
    .mf-sub{color:rgba(15,23,42,.65);font-size:.92rem}
    .mf-body{padding:20px}
    .form-control{border-radius:12px}
    .btn{border-radius:12px}
    .mf-kv{font-size:.92rem;color:rgba(15,23,42,.75)}
    .mf-kv b{color:rgba(15,23,42,.90)}
    details summary{cursor:pointer}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="mf-shell">
    <div class="mf-card">
      <div class="mf-head">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-start justify-content-between gap-3">
          <div>
            <div class="mf-logo"><i class="bi bi-shield-lock fs-4"></i> MedFlow</div>
            <div class="mf-sub">Vérification de sécurité (2FA)</div>
          </div>
          <a class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary" href="{{ path('app_logout') }}" title="Se déconnecter">
            <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-right me-1"></i> Quitter
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mf-body">
        {% for label, messages in app.flashes %}
          {% for message in messages %}
            <div class="alert alert-{{ label }}">{{ message }}</div>
          {% endfor %}
        {% endfor %}

        <p class="mb-2">Entrez le code à 6 chiffres de votre application d’authentification.</p>
        <div class="mf-kv mb-3"><b>Compte:</b> {{ account ?? (app.user.emailUser ?? app.user.userIdentifier ?? '—') }}</div>

        <form method="post" action="{{ path('app_2fa_verify') }}">
          <div class="mb-3">
            <label class="form-label fw-semibold">Code</label>
            <input name="code" class="form-control" inputmode="numeric" autocomplete="one-time-code" maxlength="12" placeholder="123456" autofocus required />
            <div class="form-text">Astuce: vous pouvez coller un code avec espace/"-" (ex: 123 456).</div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-check mb-3">
            <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" value="1" id="remember_device" name="remember_device">
            <label class="form-check-label" for="remember_device">
              Faire confiance à cet appareil pendant {{ remember_days|default(30) }} jours
            </label>
            <div class="form-text">À activer uniquement sur votre appareil personnel.</div>
          </div>

          <button class="btn btn-primary w-100" type="submit">
            <i class="bi bi-check2-circle me-1"></i> Valider
          </button>
        </form>

        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mt-3">
          <a class="link-secondary" href="{{ path('app_logout') }}">
            Changer de compte
          </a>
          <a class="link-secondary" href="{{ path('app_logout') }}">Se déconnecter</a>
        </div>

        <hr class="my-4">

        <details>
          <summary class="fw-semibold">Besoin d’aide ?</summary>
          <div class="mt-2 text-muted" style="font-size:.95rem">
            <ul class="mb-0">
              <li>Vérifiez que vous utilisez l’entrée <b>MedFlow</b> dans votre application.</li>
              <li>Attendez le prochain code si le timer est presque terminé.</li>
              <li>Si ça échoue souvent, activez la synchronisation de l’heure sur votre téléphone.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="{{ asset('assets/vendor/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js') }}"></script>
</body>
</html>
